ae58.png?fit=bounds\u0026quality=85\u0026width=1280","user":{"id":11406078,"key":"92d14522f5fb59c45086de9673cc5587","name":"のえしろ","urlname":"noeshiro","nickname":"のえしろ","userProfileImagePath":"https://assets.st-note.com/production/uploads/images/264812878/profile_2d7701653176404ed156b95d7f3048f7.jpeg?fit=bounds\u0026format=jpeg\u0026quality=85\u0026width=330","customDomain":null,"disableSupport":false,"disableGuestPurchase":false,"emailConfirmedFlag":true,"likeAppealText":null,"likeAppealImage":null,"purchaseAppealTextNote":null,"twitterNickname":null,"shareAppeal":{"text":null,"image":null},"magazineAddAppeal":{"text":null,"image":null}},"canRead":true,"isAuthor":false,"externalUrl":null,"customDomain":null,"body":"めちゃくちゃ唐突なんですけど、最近小説執筆に挑戦しています…！\n\nきっかけ\n\n今更なんですけど、最近リゼロにどハマりして（リゼロ2で3万発出たのがきっかけだなんて口が裂けても言えない…）\n\nめちゃくちゃ面白くて、1週間でアニメ全話見て、小説版も最新話まで追いついちゃいました。\n\n読んでるうちに「自分も物語作ってみたい」って思ったのがきっかけです。\n\n作ってみたい話\n\n因習村？系の話書きたいなと思ってます。\n\nアニメ・ゲームだとひぐらしのなく頃に、映画だとノロイとか、そういう話","separator":null,"isLimited":false,"isTrial":false,"canUpdate":false,"tweetText":"","twitterRelatedAccounts":"note_PR","isRefund":false,"isLiked":false,"commentCount":0,"likes":[],"anonymousLikeCount":0,"disableComment":false,"hashtags":[{"hashtag":{"name":"#小説"}},{"hashtag":{"name":"#創作"}},{"hashtag":{"name":"#創作活動"}}],"twitterShareUrl":"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://note.com/noeshiro/n/n5908acdb7482\u0026text=%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AC%E3%82%92%E6%9B%B8%E3%81%8D%E5%A7%8B%E3%82%81%E3%81%A6%E3%81%BF%E3%81%9F%EF%BD%9C%E3%81%AE%E3%81%88%E3%81%97%E3%82%8D\u0026related=note_PR","facebookShareUrl":"https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https://note.com/noeshiro/n/n5908acdb7482\u0026t=%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AC%E3%82%92%E6%9B%B8%E3%81%8D%E5%A7%8B%E3%82%81%E3%81%A6%E3%81%BF%E3%81%9F%EF%BD%9C%E3%81%AE%E3%81%88%E3%81%97%E3%82%8D%EF%BD%9Cnote%EF%BC%88%E3%83%8E%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%EF%BC%89","lineShareUrl":"https://line.naver.jp/R/msg/text/?%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AC%E3%82%92%E6%9B%B8%E3%81%8D%E5%A7%8B%E3%82%81%E3%81%A6%E3%81%